<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1942-07-08T05:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1942-07-08T05:00:00-05:00" n="413" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d413">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">893.5151/898: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Gauss</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to
                                the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Chungking</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1942-07-08T17:00:00+07:00">July 8,
                                    1942—5 p.m.</date>
                                <lb/> [Received July 9—4:44 a.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>813. For Secretary of Treasury from Adler.</p>
                        <p>TF–49. Board at meeting today, which chairman invited me to attend as
                            observer, decided to change its official rate for Chinese national
                            currency to 5<hi rend="superscript">1/16</hi> United States cents and
                                3<hi rend="superscript">1/64</hi> pence to be effective <pb facs="0540" n="530" xml:id="pg_530"/> as from the opening of
                            business July 10. Banks selling rate will be 5 United States cents and 3
                            pence. [Adler.]</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Gauss</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>